What will demo (in 8 steps)
Developer push → GitHub.
CI (Jenkins or GitHub Actions): lint + unit tests → build & push Docker image.
AI code review on PR and AI release notes in CI.
GitOps: Argo CD auto-syncs app to a local Kubernetes (kind) cluster.
Monitoring: Prometheus + Grafana; app exposes /metrics .
Synthetic load to trigger metrics.
AI log triage / metrics summary from your terminal.
Post‑deploy smoke tests and quick rollback via Git.
